latestPosts.caption:
Capturing 16 Years of Love in Just 5 Minutes.

Join us on a journey from our first date to the deep bond we share today, as we prepare to say “I do.”

From our school days to building our careers together, the road hasn’t always been easy. Navigating the challenge of convincing our parents to support our love—especially since we grew up in the same neighborhood—was no small feat.

But through it all, one thing has remained certain: our unwavering commitment to each other.

Watch Bhaswati and Nitu’s beautiful journey unfold in this video!
